data.description:
Your search is over with this stunning brick-front two-story home, prominently located on a corner lot in the highly desirable Northridge Heights neighborhood in the Gilbert School District. This residence boasts a harmonious blend of comfort and sophistication, with ample space to accommodate both everyday living and grand entertaining.
Featuring five generously sized bedrooms and four bathrooms, this home is perfectly suited for a growing family or hosting guests. The spacious owner's suite is a true retreat, complete with custom soaker tub, his and hers closets, and serene views of the landscaped yard.  The 5th Bedroom is as generous as primary suite located in the lower level with it's own bath and walk in closet.
A chef's delight, the kitchen offers extensive workspace, modern appliances, and ample storage. It's an ideal setting for casual family meals or large gatherings, seamlessly integrating functionality with style.  
This property boasts an impressive array of living spaces, including three designated living areas and a dedicated formal dining room, and an informal dining space adjacent to the kitchen perfect for hosting dinner parties and special events.
Enjoy the comfort and appeal of new carpeting upstairs and luxurious new LVP flooring on the main level, both chosen to enhance the home's aesthetics and durability.  
Bonus space on the main floor perfect for remote work or study, music room or anything else your imagination can think of!  This space  offers privacy and quiet away from the home's main living areas.The built-in bar in the basement sets the stage for memorable entertainment, providing a stylish and inviting atmosphere for gatherings and celebrations.
Schools, parks, shopping, and dining options are all within easy reach, ensuring a lifestyle of convenience and quality.
Call me today to schedule your private viewing.
